%example
s(s(a,SA,b)) --> [a],s(SA),[b].
s(s(epsilon)) --> [].
%example call: s(L,['a','a','b','b'],S).
% L = s(a, s(a, s(epsilon), b), b),
% S = [] 


% DCG grammar from the first part of the project
exp --> sub_exp, ['|'], exp.

exp --> sub_exp.

sub_exp --> term, sub_exp.
sub_exp --> term.

term --> sub_term, ['*'].
term --> sub_term.

sub_term --> char.
sub_term --> ['.'].
sub_term --> ['('], exp, [')'].

char --> [X], {X\=='.',X\=='*',
            X\=='(',X\==')',X\=='|',
            char_type(X,ascii)}.
